Source.Name: qt6-declarative
Source.Summary: Classes for QML and JavaScript languages
Source.Description: The Qt Quick module is the standard library for writing QML applications. While the Qt QML module provides the QML engine and language infrastructure, the Qt Quick module provides all the basic types necessary for creating user interfaces with QML.
